# Studio Media Tanzania Website - Project Summary

## üéØ Project Overview

A professional, responsive website for Studio Media Tanzania - a photography, videography, editing, and printing services company based in Dar es Salaam, Tanzania.

**Developer**: Revocatus Kajana
**Email**: revocajana@gmail.com
**Technology Stack**: PHP + Bootstrap + MySQL

## ‚úÖ Completed Features

### üè† Homepage (`index.php`)
- **Hero Section**: Eye-catching banner with call-to-action buttons
- **Services Overview**: Cards showcasing photography, videography, editing, and printing
- **Portfolio Preview**: Sample work with hover effects
- **Call-to-Action**: Encouraging visitors to book sessions

### üñºÔ∏è Portfolio Page (`portfolio.php`)
- **Filterable Gallery**: Categories for wedding, portrait, event, commercial, and video
- **Interactive Modals**: Detailed view of portfolio items
- **Video Integration**: Support for video portfolio items
- **Responsive Grid**: Works perfectly on all devices

### üõ†Ô∏è Services Page (`services.php`)
- **Detailed Service Listings**: Photography, videography, editing, printing
- **Pricing Information**: Transparent pricing for all services
- **Service Packages**: Basic, Premium, and Luxury packages
- **Package Comparison**: Clear feature comparison

### üìÖ Booking System (`booking.php`)
- **Comprehensive Form**: Name, contact, service type, event details
- **Package Selection**: Integration with service packages
- **Database Storage**: All bookings saved to database
- **Email Notifications**: Automatic emails to admin
- **Form Validation**: Client and server-side validation

### üìû Contact Page (`contact.php`)
- **Contact Form**: Subject-based inquiry system
- **Business Information**: Address, phone, email, hours
- **Google Maps**: Interactive map integration
- **FAQ Section**: Answers to common questions
- **Social Media Links**: Easy access to social profiles

### üí¨ Testimonials Page (`testimonials.php`)
- **Client Reviews**: Showcase of satisfied customers
- **Rating System**: 5-star rating display
- **Add Review Modal**: Allow clients to submit testimonials
- **Statistics Section**: Client count, projects, rating average
- **Responsive Cards**: Beautiful testimonial display

### üîê Admin System
- **Admin Login** (`admin/login.php`): Secure authentication system
- **Session Management**: Secure admin sessions
- **Activity Logging**: Track admin actions
- **Password Security**: Bcrypt hashing

### üóÑÔ∏è Database Structure
- **Comprehensive Schema**: 11 tables for full functionality
- **Relationships**: Proper foreign key relationships
- **Security**: Prepared statements, input sanitization
- **Scalability**: Designed for growth

### üé® Design & UX
- **Responsive Design**: Perfect on mobile, tablet, desktop
- **Bootstrap 5**: Modern, professional styling
